flowchart TD
  start([Push to main]) --> install[Install deps]
  install --> lint{Lint passes?}
  lint -->|yes| test[Run tests]
  lint -->|no| fail[(Report failure)]
  test --> build[Build artifacts]
  build --> deploy{{Deploy?}}
  deploy -- prod --> prod[/Ship to prod/]
  deploy -- staging --> stg[\Ship to staging\]
  prod --> done((Done))
  stg --> done
  fail --> done

  classDef bad fill:#fde8e8,stroke:#d9534f,color:#611
  class fail bad
